    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EVERCHAINED 1.1 - 1 YEAR UPDATE IS OUT!</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>KEYBOARD ONLY</strong> and <strong>GAMEPAD</strong> support!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BALANCING</strong> to sword swings and boss fights!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>LOCALIZATION</strong> framework to support multiple languages in the future!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>In countless timelines, lands have been devastated by Master's invasion, again and again...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>...and now you're here to perfect it.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EVERCHAINED</strong> is a boss-rush, souls-lite game where you challenge bosses through various paths to choose, featuring dodge-based combat and a unique take on handling your greatsword.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010450/extras/1b3e7381fb80baf9ff3b864162d8303d.poster.avif?t=1757026793\" width=640 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010450/extras/1b3e7381fb80baf9ff3b864162d8303d.webm?t=1757026793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010450/extras/1b3e7381fb80baf9ff3b864162d8303d.mp4?t=1757026793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>16 BOSS FIGHTS</strong> from monolithic giants to eldritch horrors.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>32 TRINKETS</strong> granting powerful perks to master the journey with a build of your own.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>STAT UPGRADES</strong> to spend shards on, collected with consecutive hits of your greatsword.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SCALING NG+</strong> to test your skills against tougher versions of each encounter.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>All accompanied by:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A stylized look inspired by early 2000s' Flash games, <strong>fitted in a scalable 4:3 aspect ratio.</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original orchestral/synth soundtrack, <strong>consisting a new track for each fight.</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Achievements <strong>to collect and show off your expertise.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Soul of the Great Hero..</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>With your wit and strength, the Great Return is inevitable...</i></p>",
